      <title>特朗普对加拿大、墨西哥征收关税威胁提振美元，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对加拿大和墨西哥征收 25% 的进口关税后，美元上涨，黄金价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-26/gold-falls-as-trump-tariff-threat-on-canada-mexico-aids-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Nov 2024 00:32:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
